SIMULATION architecture:

OrderBook
    ↓
MarketStateProvider
    ↓
MarketMaker Agent
    ↓
MarketMakerRunner
    ↓
Matching Engine

Every 100 milliseconds:
1. Read MarketState
2. Agent decides action
3. Generate synthetic orders
4. Submit orders to engine